AFFORDABLE

• Secure payouts to your bank account

creator: SumUp
descriptionHtml:
THIS IS HOW YOU GET STARTED
1. Download the SumUp App an create a free SumUp Account
2. Order the SumUp PIN+ Card Terminal
3. Accept card payments right away

THIS IS HOW YOU ACCEPT CARD PAYMENTS WITH SUMUP
1. Enter amount in the SumUp App
2. Insert the customer’s card into the SumUp PIN+ Card Terminal
3. Your customer approves the payment by entering his PIN
Optionally, you can send a receipt via text message or email or print it out.


AFFORDABLE
• No monthly fees, no monthly commitment, no contract runtime
• Only pay when actively using SumUp: 1,95% per transaction
• Accept all debit (VPay, Maestro) and credit cards (Visa, MasterCard, UK only: American Express)
• Secure payouts to your bank account


SECURE
SumUp is authorised as a Payment Institution by the Financial Conduct Authority and is Europay, MasterCard, and Visa (EMV) and PCI-DSS certified, ensuring that payments are processed in accordance with the highest security standards.


JOIN THE SUMUP COMMUNITY OF HAPPY MERCHANTS
“SumUp offers us everything we need: a fair cost, full mobility, and practically more sales since our customers are not dependant on how much cash they carry anymore.“ Moritz Biel & André Hofmann - Stoffbruch, Designer Streetwear


More: https://sumup.com
descriptionShort: Accept card payments with your smartphone/tablet and boost your sales.
